<h1>About Snake Game</h1>

<p>
    This Snake Game is a real-time multiplayer experience where players connect to a central server and interact within a shared game world. Each player controls a snake that moves continuously across the map. Every snake is displayed in a unique color, allowing players to easily distinguish themselves from others. The player’s name and current score are rendered above their snake and update dynamically as the game progresses.
</p>

<h2>Gameplay</h2>
<p>
    The core gameplay includes controlling your snake and surviving as long as possible while competing against other players. Once connected, your snake begins moving automatically, and you must guide it using keyboard input. The main objectives are:
</p>

<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Collect power-ups:</strong> Power-ups appear throughout the map and increase your score when collected. Successfully gathering them helps you grow longer.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Avoid collisions:</strong> Colliding with walls or any snake (including your own body or other players) will result in your snake being eliminated.
    </li>
</ul>

<h2>Features</h2>

<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Explosion effects:</strong> When a player is eliminated, a visual explosion effect is displayed at the location of their snake’s death.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Keyboard controls:</strong> Players can control their snake using either the WASD keys or the arrow keys.
    </li>
</ul>

